title: What font is this? From printed letter
content:
Hello, guys.

Do you have any idea what is the name of this font?

![](http://web.archive.org/web/20150417081706im_/http:/kamiennik.nazwa.pl/font.png)

Please note that it is not Courier or Courier New, nor American Typewriter. I've compared this three and there's no exact match. It is something in between.

Thanks in advance for your help.

(Sorry if my english is not perfect.)
author: LukaszKamiennik
